metadata.name: Death and Honour
metadata.description:
We die to live again, death comes yet not totally when life is taken out of you. Death to the physical things, death to what happens along your journey in life. 

The death you need to die might be people talking you down, pulling you down on your way up, death to not seeing all these always keep you focus on your goals. 

Death to self weakness helps build you through the journey of life. This death are what brings you the honor at the end of it all.
